{"tid":1162452,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"六百萬fullpay包裝修 買邊到好 荃灣區","createTime":"2019-05-20T01:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T08:38:56.000Z","uid":16974,"like":5,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"081e268ec005b1f332fff62bccac11ffd21ac2e9","tid":1162452,"uid":16974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:22:21.000Z","msg":"如果渣住六百萬係手 荃灣 葵盛嗰邊啲地區買邊到好<br />\n唔係太介意樓舊啲啲 因為想預啲錢黎做裝修同間房 <br />\n有冇ching有啲咩好提議<br />\n我自己上網睇左葵星中心好似較平同四正 但有冇伏？<br />\n另外想問下如果將廚房改做房 間過啲牆有冇問題？我做research知道如果要郁廚廁走喉好麻煩 所以唔諗住郁廁 剩係改廚房做房 另外係廚做返個開放式廚房 需唔需要近返原本個廚房位走喉？<br />\n450尺換哂啲地板 間牆同整個開放式廚房洗唔洗三十萬？唔洗設計<br />\n另外改則係咪要申請 第一次睇依啲想問清楚啲 麻煩哂咁多位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b127f1a81a8668e064c7a31676c5a18bf6dad8","tid":1162452,"uid":115337,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔做少少按揭？"},{"pid":"d437a83728290d0980504bbfb15c5cc661f0fc03","tid":1162452,"uid":82068,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"你真係發撚緊夢"},{"pid":"28356077263bfabada35f372c270ae7d5ef90845","tid":1162452,"uid":985,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"600萬，裝修當30，買料傢私10萬，電器5萬，稅10零萬，仲有500零萬，450呎唔買大西北仲不咩選擇"},{"pid":"2d9838a059d0e2663c5b8cd6e4f2d5da059f12b7","tid":1162452,"uid":129658,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"6球野搵銀行借買8-9球樓供都得啦"},{"pid":"58f2601324b03730321b5460f85dee594d958664","tid":1162452,"uid":251529,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d8d4ba42dadc8d36e6793a91d83cb5a6eb7cab8","tid":1162452,"uid":16974,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"2d9838a059d0e2663c5b8cd6e4f2d5da059f12b7","tid":1162452,"uid":129658,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:32:49.0